    Localization helpers
    ResourceBundleFileManager
    A resource manager class for ResourceBundle implementation based on property files not present in the classpath which can't be instantiated with the ResourceBundle.getBundle(resourceName, locale); (for example near the report templates)
    ResourceBundleManager
    Used to have access to resource bundles outside of struts
    ResourceBundleProperties
    An implementation o ResourceBundle over properties
